  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a bed height make an effect to endotracheal
      intubation with Macintosh laryngoscope, Glidescope and Airwayscope during chest compressions
      in- hospital simulation cardiac arrest.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
